<br>
Those of you who know me, know I have always been an approachable, friendly player. I answer every question that any player asks me regarding the paladin class. I make time to help people, people I don't even know in many cases. I don't have a single person on my ignore list, and as far as I know am not on anyone elses. <br>
<br>
Yet someone had nothing better to do but take a shot at me. I don't understand why someone would be so fucking petty.<br>
<br>
I am livid at the moment and feel fucking cheated.<br>
<br>
And if I ever find out who did this, I promise , they will be petitioning me alot more often.<br>
<br>
