<br>
The sad thing is, my sk's name is a clear violation of the naming convention. Yet, I have been approached by 2-3 gm's as well as guides. Hell the lead GM of the game's alert team( you know the ones who cover the servers late at night when the normal GM's are gone) tell me it was a very inventive name and gave me a /clap /cheer for it. <br>
<br>
It's disgusting how petty people can be about names. It also pisses me off when players come up and tell me &quot;You know your name is a violation?&quot;. Of course it is, but several staff members have given me a pat on the back for thinking it up. <br>
<br>
